        <zone flipboard-zone-id='5' forceUpdate='true' h='79951' id='13' story-point-id='8' type-v2='text' w='97201' x='1527' y='18949'>
          <formatted-text>
            <run bold='true' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12' underline='true'>Final Business Recommendations</run>
            <run>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Profit Optimization</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Reduce heavy discounts to improve profit.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Monitor refund-heavy categories closely.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Improve pricing strategy after June decline.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Store Performance</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Improve performance of low-margin stores.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Maintain stock availability in high-sales stores.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Reduce return rates through better quality control.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Promotions</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Continue promotions that increase both sales and profit.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Stop promotions that increase volume but reduce margins.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Supply Chain &amp; Inventory</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Reduce vendor delivery delays.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Maintain safety stock for important products.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Improve inventory planning to avoid stockouts.</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Overall Strategic Insight</run>
            <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
            <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book' fontsize='12'>Profit declined after June due to discount leakage, refunds, stockouts, and vendor delays. Better monitoring across sales, promotions, inventory, and supply chain can improve profitability and operational efficiency.</run>
          </formatted-text>
        </zone>
      </zones>
      <simple-id uuid='{64F84736-47A9-4891-8B90-5301203913A5}' />
    </dashboard>
